267
00:13:03,333 --> 00:13:04,166
[gasps]

268
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:07,083
[MAIA]
Monitor Akira Kaibuki.

269
00:13:07,166 --> 00:13:09,416
There's been no further
word since Master Sougon

270
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:10,958
