you just might make it!

316
00:15:00,958 --> 00:15:04,791
[TSUTOMU]
Miss Sakurako! You're my savior!

317
00:15:04,875 --> 00:15:06,041
[AKIRA]
You called?

318
00:15:07,166 --> 00:15:09,083
