381
00:17:50,791 --> 00:17:52,541
[AKIRA]
Frozen solid.

382
00:17:52,625 --> 00:17:53,708
No! Dammit!

383
00:17:53,791 --> 00:17:56,833
I wanna see those
swimsuits! Swim! Suits!

384
00:17:56,916 --> 00:17:58,583
