please be serious?

387
00:18:02,458 --> 00:18:04,083
I'm super-mega serious!

388
00:18:04,166 --> 00:18:05,500
[HAYATO]
No, you're an idiot!

389
00:18:05,583 --> 00:18:09,666
[SAKURAKO growls] Cut it out,
that's an order! Now!

390
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:12,125
